name: Milkmaid Wood Boul
detail: Our wooden Supreme offer customers distinguished, natural looks to fit both indoor and outdoor uses. With a variety of light and dark wood tones, our wooden planter options can mesh with your surrounding wood finishes or stand out with a statement wood tone.

name: Ruched Wood Jar
detail: This hand-made round storage jar is crafted to replicate the antique wood used by village artisans to holding wheat, rice, and other foods from the local street markets as a storage container, these types of jars were primarily used during barter transactions.

name: Ball candle holder
detail: Ball candle holder from Swedish brand Cooee Design which makes each piece unique and has a smooth finish which is this range's hallmark. The ball shaped candle holder comes in many different colours and sizes, which can be mixed and matched for a great look!
